Ultra-realistic studio side-profile portrait of a modern man showcasing contemporary men’s hairstyles. Clean barbershop photography style with sharp focus on haircut details and texture. Neutral male model wearing a dark hoodie, shot in profile view. Warm {argument name="background color" default="mustard–orange"} seamless background, soft diffused studio lighting with gentle shadows to emphasize fade transitions and hair texture. Natural skin tones, visible hair strands, crisp edges, professional grooming aesthetic, high-resolution DSLR look, shallow depth of field, editorial haircut reference photography.

Hair style modifiers (swap as needed):

{argument name="hair style 1" default="high fade with textured top"}

{argument name="hair style 2" default="short textured crop with low fade"}

messy textured quiff with fade

modern mullet with layered texture

